<Author>UBishopsCanada
<Content>Good Option Out East! Smaller, modern hotel in eastern part of Berlin, one block from U-Bahn to everywhere with S Bahn and DB trains close by. Excellent bar and restaurant on ground floor. Credit card activated internet in lobby. Room very comfortable with modern bath. Please note: Tub shower is quite high and may be difficult for some to enter or leave without help. Very nice experience overall.Only anxiety provoking moment was on check out when desk clerk had no information that stay had already been paid for on Orbitz. After 10 minutes it was cleared up but keep your web confirmation with you and I would advise this be addressed on check-in to avoid embarassing or anxious incident when cab is waiting for airport, 
