<Author>CornwallTizzie
<Content>Highly recommended The hotel was very good value for money. The breakfast was excellent and the situation was ideal with great transport links into central Berlin. We stayed here on our first visit to Berlin - we would love to go back and would have no qualms about staying in this hotel again. The only slight draw back was that it is by a busy road but thats to be expected in a city. However the room had great blinds and aircon. Quick tip - instead of raiding the minibar we found an Aldi supermarket in the nearby shopping arcade so stocked up on goodies there and used the fridge in the room. 
